COMP106 Assignment 4

************************
Compiling and Executing:
javac Main.java
java Main

************************
Features:

StatePanel:
1. Coordinates of selected cell
2. maximum combo chain size
3. score and level

ControlPanel:
1. (re)start a game
2. cheat and add 500 points!
3. exit the game

Sound:
1. selection sound
2. falling sound

Animation:
1. swapping animation
2. cascading animation

************************
Program Design:
 
   The architecture of this program differs little from the 
previous assignment. The only addition is the Animation class to
help implement swapping and cascading of jewels.


